 class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推過關FATFAT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似話支那第四季外國廢紙未有批文。所以無貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6ffacdacf579b57c578015527e5ac785bf8773","tid":389290,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸紙價升到上天喎</blockquote><br />\n點解貴咗咁多<br />\n支那紙皮呢幾年成日加價"},{"pid":"4031f7905e80eb338e8742da917395af058a26e8","tid":389290,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大陸紙價升到上天喎</blockquote><br />\n點解貴咗咁多<br />\n支那紙皮呢幾年成日加價</blockquote><br />\n回收廢紙一定有得做；香港自已投資造囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba8e1c8aaeed1dccaeb09a30ea5a0f77a4f6cee","tid":389290,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大陸紙價升到上天喎</blockquote><br />\n點解貴咗咁多<br />\n支那紙皮呢幾年成日加價</blockquote><br />\n回收廢紙一定有得做；香港自已投資造囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港係廢物轉運去支那。一唔收已經出事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}